#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.18"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.18:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.18:0.2"
msgid "2. Rathakāravagga"
msgstr "2. The Chariotmaker"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.18:0.3"
msgid "18. Devalokasutta"
msgstr "18. The Realm of the Gods"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.115"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.18:1.1"
msgid "“Sace vo, bhikkhave, aññatitthiyā paribbājakā evaṃ puccheyyuṃ:"
msgstr "“Mendicants, if wanderers who follow another path were to ask you:"

msgctxt "an3.18:1.2"
msgid "‘devalokūpapattiyā, āvuso, samaṇe gotame brahmacariyaṃ vussathā’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘Reverend, do you live the spiritual life with the ascetic Gotama so that "
"you can be reborn in the realm of the gods?’"

msgctxt "an3.18:1.3"
msgid ""
"Nanu tumhe, bhikkhave, evaṃ puṭṭhā aṭṭīyeyyātha harāyeyyātha "
"jiguccheyyāthā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Being questioned like this, wouldn’t you be horrified, embarrassed, and "
"disgusted?”"

msgctxt "an3.18:1.4"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Yes, sir.”"

msgctxt "an3.18:1.5"
msgid ""
"“Iti kira tumhe, bhikkhave, dibbena āyunā aṭṭīyatha harāyatha jigucchatha, "
"dibbena vaṇṇena dibbena sukhena dibbena yasena dibbenādhipateyyena aṭṭīyatha "
"harāyatha jigucchatha;"
msgstr ""
"“So it seems that you are horrified, repelled, and disgusted by divine "
"lifespan, beauty, happiness, fame, and power."

msgctxt "an3.18:1.6"
msgid ""
"pageva kho pana, bhikkhave, tumhehi kāyaduccaritena aṭṭīyitabbaṃ "
"harāyitabbaṃ jigucchitabbaṃ, vacīduccaritena … manoduccaritena aṭṭīyitabbaṃ "
"harāyitabbaṃ jigucchitabban”ti."
msgstr ""
"How much more then should you be horrified, embarrassed, and disgusted by "
"bad conduct by way of body, speech, and mind.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.18:1.7"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
